4. It Improves Audience Orientation and Retention
Outlining supports a logical flow that aligns with how audiences process information â€” beginning, development, and conclusion.
This cognitive scaffolding enhances comprehension and retention of presented material.
References
Nature / Scitable. (2020). Oral Presentation Structure. Retrieved from https://www.nature.com/scitable/topicpage/oral-presentation-structure-13900387
Prezent.ai. (2023). A Guide on Creating an Effective Presentation Outline. Retrieved from https://www.prezent.ai/blog/presentation-outline
